          "Notable Quotes"
        ]
      },
      "value": {
        "none": [
          "\"Tomatoes are grown in the target area during the winter, spring and early summer. This is a rain-sensitive crop, particularly during ripening stage. Obviously increased rainfall from seeding at this time would have an adverse effect on this crop.\" — Impact Assessment Through 1980"
